:eco:  Every week at Eco we hold an ‘*all hands*’ meetings where the whole team gathers to discuss the highlights of the week, projects we're working on and upcoming developments. 

An important part of these meetings is naming Eco’s “*Unsung Hero*”. 

Each week, our CEO Andy identifies a team member and highlights something that they've done over the past 7 days which may have initially been overlooked but which goes above and beyond the call of duty and is worth drawing attention to. 

We thought it would be a good idea to do something similar here in our Eco community in order to recognize the incredible effort and support we’ve received from our amazing community members! With so much activity going on every single day in our Discord server want to make sure to call out contributions that deserve to be highlighted and celebrated.

So, each week we will nominate 5 “***Unsung Hero***” candidates from Eco community and highlight the things they did to help the *E-community* through their leadership, creativity or technical skills. 

Everyone will then have 5 days to vote and choose the person they feel is most deserving of the Eco “***Unsung Hero***” title. The Eco team will choose 1 winner as well.

Nominees will be announced on Mondays mornings and voting will run until Friday at 5pm EST.

As always, thank you so much to all the amazing *Ecolytes* in this *Eco-mmunity*. We are constantly humbled by the incredible group of people that have chosen to share this journey with us! :eco_heart:

We would also like to give a special shoutout to @Crypto for being the first to propose this idea to the Eco Team!

#votehere

** Week 1 Candidates**

🟪 @Restyle 
Creator of some of the most incredible images / videos to come out of the #🧪meme-lab , (as well as being the creator of the next-level “stomp” Eco promo video) Restyle has made a visual and aesthetic mark on the *Eco-mmunity* like no other!

🟩 @Anjin_san 
If you’ve used an emoji on the Eco server it’s more than likely that Anjin_san made it! Creator of the now universally adopted :points: Points emoji (among many others) Anjin_San has perhaps done more than any other member to help develop the aesthetic of the Eco Discord Server through their quality artistic contributions! Beyond that, Anjin_San is a highly active community member both in the #🚀general  and language specific channels!

🟨 @parallacs 
You can’t scroll through any channel in the Eco Discord server for more than a second or two without finding a contribution from parallacs. Present everywhere, always helpful and full of good ideas (they gave us the idea for the #🔎history-submissions  channel) parallacs has been a key contributor to the *Eco-mmunity* since day 1.

🟥 @Crypto 
Eco’s unofficial “welcoming party,” community guide and the very reason that the #🦸eco-unsung-heroes  program exists, Crypto has played an important role in building the positive, informed and engaged community that Eco is blessed with today. 

🟦 @Redallica 
A core contributor in both the language and developer channels, Redallica is everywhere! Positive, helpful and incredibly keen to help build the *Eco-mmunity*, Redallica (among many other things) also led the creation of the French Eco Website!

#votehere

**Week 2 Candidates**

🟪 @KingSuper 
From Day 1 KingSuper has played a key part of the Eco-mmunity. Always present with a helpful insight, positive comment or valuable feedback, you know by their signature *suspepe* :peepohappy: emoji that KingSuper is always watching out for us! 

🟩 @Saurois 
Saurious has been an important contributor and been actively involved in almost every important development in the Eco Discord server. From helping develop governance proposals to creating incredible memes and content bounty submissions, Saurios is an incredible member of the *Eco-mmunity*! 

🟨 @JCoin 
A relatively new member, JCoin has nonetheless already made a mark on the Eco Discord by way of some great ideas (i.e. an Eco Hackathon) and moving insights (check out the "Alien Market" discussion in #🧮eco-nomics ) 

🟥 @mini 
Mini has taken the time to put together a fantastic Chinese transcript of the past few live audio community event. A huge amount of work goes into producing these transcripts so that people can learn about Eco in other languages! :eco_heart: 

🟦 @Exarare 
Exarare has produced some of the most thought provoking and insightful content to come out of the *Eco-community* since their arrival. While focusing mainly on the #🧮eco-nomics channel, Exarare will often pop into other areas of governance or community to drop a pearl of wisdom or a probing question!

***Please note:** In order to cast a vote, users need the “**Voter**” role. If you don't have it simply DM any member of the Eco Team. Thank you all for your participation.*

#votehere

**Week 3 Candidates**

🟪 @SimplyClassic 
For consistently high production value #🏅content-bounties  submissions, utilizing laser cutting and fabrication skills as well as great video editing skills!

🟩 @amahodler 
For creating polished #🏅content-bounties  submissions and rallying a team behind them. (Ferris wheel eco logo, Queco duck mascot and many more!)

🟨 @Saulo 
For playing an important role in the development of Eco #📜governance  initiatives, committing hours of effort toward maintaining the integrity of the voting process in the Eco Discord and for acting as the “conscience” of the *Eco-mmunity*.

🟥 @one2fckU 
For being the first user to suggest, submit and be approved for the newly created #🤝community-bounties  channel where users can submit their own ideas for bounties in the Eco Discord. Also for creating some of the coolest bounty submissions we’ve seen yet! 

🟦 @salova 
For being another member of the community deeply engaged in the development of #📜governance  proposals and working tirelessly to ensure bounties / voting initiatives are conducted transparently. Salova also played an important role in developing the Eco-Quiz which has been enjoyed by hundreds of community members!

#votehere

**Week 4 Candidates**

🟪 @Jeremie  - @Jeremie  does much of the coordinating (as well as actively participating) in the #📜governance  groups. Jeremie is also an integral part of a group that is working hard to maintain the voting integrity of the Eco Discord and is an active participant in the :eco:  #🇫🇷fr-eco  channel.

🟩 @bsori7771  - @bsori7771  is everywhere in the #🚀general  channel and is always around to help answer new users' questions and direct them to the right places. Beyond that, they contribute regularly to the #🏅content-bounties  and do some killer raccoon 🦝  mascots to boot! 

🟨 @passenger  - Wherever you are in the Eco Discord, @passenger  is there. They play an integral role in the operation of almost every part of the *Eco-mmunity*. Passenger answers questions, organizes language managers and keeps content up to date across the :eco:  server.

🟥 @Mercurius Caduceus - Responsible for setting up our brand new #🇩🇪dach-eco🇦🇹🇨🇭🇱🇺🇱🇮  channel, @Mercurius Caduceus  is a relatively new member of the :eco:  Discord but has quickly set to work helping to grow the *Eco-mmunity* and spread the word to new audiences. 

🟦 @EcoJP (EJ) - Another relatively new member who has nonetheless made their presence felt almost immediately, @EcoJP (EJ)  is responsible for the creation and maintenance of the :eco: #🇯🇵jp-eco channel!

Please note: In order to cast a vote, users need the “Voter” role. If you don't have it simply DM any member of the Eco Team. Thank you all for your participation.

#votehere

**Week 5 Candidates**

🟪 @AkaKwak🦆  is everyones favourite 🦆  (sorry Donald 😉 ) and is always around to help new users in the Eco Discord by answering questions, acting as our unofficial ‘*welcoming committee*’ and contributing to the great atmosphere of the *Eco-mmunity*.

**Please note:** In order to cast a vote, users need the “Voter” role. If you don't have it simply DM any member of the Eco Team. Thank you all for your participation.

#votehere

#votehere

🟩 @SpaceTraveler  is another relatively new member of our *Eco-mmunity* but they have made it their mission to help every new member get started with :eco: and answer any questions they may have. @SpaceTraveler  is also heavily involved in governance initiatives and educational efforts.
